2. Exclusions
a. This endorsement does not apply to:
i. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the rendering or
failure to render professional services, including but not limited to
medical, dental, legal, or accounting services;
ii. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the sale,
distribution, or manufacture of products, including food products;
iii. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the ownership,
maintenance, or use of motor vehicles, aircraft, or watercraft, except as

provided in Section I of the policy;
iv. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the rental of the
"residence premises" or any portion thereof to others;
v. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the conduct of any
business not described in Section 1.a. above;
vi. Bodily injury or property damage for which the "insured" is covered
under a workers' compensation, disability benefits, or similar law;
vii. Bodily injury or property damage arising out of the failure of any
product or service sold, distributed, or manufactured by the home-based
business to perform as intended or warranted.

1. No Coverage for Certain Losses. This endorsement does not insure
against:

a. Loss caused by flood, tidal wave, or tsunami, even if generated by an
earthquake;
b. Land subsidence, landslide, mudslide, or sinkhole, unless directly
caused by an earthquake as defined herein;
c. Cost of filling land, grading, or excavating unless required to
restore the dwelling to its pre-loss condition;
d. Loss to exterior masonry, parapets, or ornamentation unless part of a
covered structure;
e. Loss to awnings, outdoor equipment, or detached structures unless
specifically covered under Section I – Coverage B.

